title: Brown-Last Court of Appeal(republic vs democracy,sovereignity vs
description: This is Norman E. Brown's informative booklet Last Court of Appeal which tells the story of how Americans have sold out their god-given right to true freedom and replaced it with a false "democracy" instead of a true republic of self-governing free men as their founding fathers intended. Is the democratic right to vote really equal to maintaining true freedom? What role does the militia play? What about posse comitatus & the 2nd amendment? Also includes discussions about sovereignty vs. serf, subjects vs. citizens and magna carta. 10 pages. A must read for everyone.
